8. O-O O-O 9. d3 Nd4 10. Bg5 h6 11. Bh4 g5 12. Bg3 Ng6
{ with an advantage to Black who is controlling the dark squares in the centre. He may further contemplate ...Kh7 and ...f5, to start a kingside advance. }
