f4 { then Black can play } 15... e5 16. Nf5 b5
{ obtaining excellent counterplay, since taking on d6 doesn't bring much to White after }
17. Nxd6 Qb6+ 18. Qf2 Qxf2+ 19. Rxf2 Bxd6 20. Rxd6 bxc4
{ and the endgame is sharp but good for Black. } *

